# 🧱 1. COMMAND SYSTEM (THE ONLY WRITE PATH)

Everything in the creator dashboard becomes a **command**.

---

## 🧠 COMMAND FORMAT

```json id="ct0"
{
  "type": "commandType",
  "payload": {},
  "meta": {
    "workspaceId": "graph",
    "timestamp": 123456
  }
}
```

---

## 🧠 WHY THIS MATTERS

This gives you:

* undo/redo
* replay of edits
* validation before execution
* batching
* multiplayer later
* audit trail

