# 🧱 3. COMMAND PIPELINE (CRITICAL ARCHITECTURE)

Every command follows this flow:

```txt id="ct11"
UI Action
   ↓
Command Builder
   ↓
Validation Layer
   ↓
Command Executor
   ↓
Engine Mutation
   ↓
Event Emission
   ↓
UI Sync
```

