# 🧠 4. VALIDATION CONTRACT (PRE-EXECUTION)

Before ANY command runs:

## CHECKS:

### ✔ schema validity

### ✔ node existence

### ✔ asset existence

### ✔ transition validity

### ✔ effect validity

### ✔ permissions (workspace rules)

---

## OUTPUT:

```json id="ct12"
{
  "valid": true,
  "errors": [],
  "warnings": []
}
```

---

# 🧱 5. COMMAND EXECUTION ENGINE

This is your internal router:

```txt id="ct13"
command.type → handler(command.payload)
```

---

## EXAMPLE HANDLER MAP

```js id="ct14"
const handlers = {
  "node.create": createNode,
  "node.update": updateNode,
  "node.delete": deleteNode,
